Generate CLI snapshot tests for a binary

Usage: moss generate cli-snapshot [OPTIONS] <BINARY>

Arguments:
  <BINARY>  Path to the CLI binary

Options:
  -o, --output <OUTPUT>  Output file for the test (stdout if not specified)
      --name <NAME>      Binary name to use in test (defaults to file stem)
      --json             Output as JSON
      --jq <EXPR>        Filter JSON output with jq expression (implies --json)
      --pretty           Human-friendly output with colors and formatting
      --compact          Compact output without colors (overrides TTY detection)
  -h, --help             Print help
